Again, the idiot doesn’t know how to read. Quote me, where I said Tenma was coded in PHP? All I did was mention the PHP script that Tenma uses, saying you wouldn’t have been able to even code that. Remember, you were the one who added me to come code the frontend part of your’s/dumm1s’ server.
